""SET NOCOUNT ON;
DELETE FROM [ProductImages]
WHERE [Id] = @p0;
SELECT @@ROWCOUNT;

DELETE FROM [ProductImages]
WHERE [Id] = @p1;
SELECT @@ROWCOUNT;

DELETE FROM [ProductImages]
WHERE [Id] = @p2;
SELECT @@ROWCOUNT;

DELETE FROM [ProductImages]
WHERE [Id] = @p3;
SELECT @@ROWCOUNT;

DELETE FROM [ProductImages]
WHERE [Id] = @p4;
SELECT @@ROWCOUNT;

DECLARE @inserted5 TABLE ([Id] int, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [ProductImages] USING (
VALUES (@p5, @p6, @p7, 0),
(@p8, @p9, @p10, 1),
(@p11, @p12, @p13, 2),
(@p14, @p15, @p16, 3),
(@p17, @p18, @p19, 4),
(@p20, @p21, @p22, 5)) AS i ([Caption], [Path], [ProductId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([Caption], [Path], [ProductId])
VALUES (i.[Caption], i.[Path], i.[ProductId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted5;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [ProductImages] t

    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [x.AdvertisementPosition].[PageId], [x.AdvertisementPosition].[Name] AS [Name1], CASE
    WHEN [x.AdvertisementPosition].[PageId] IS NOT NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [x.AdvertisementPosition.AdvertisementPage].[Id] AS [Id0], [x.AdvertisementPosition.AdvertisementPage].[Name] AS [Name0]
FROM [Advertisements] AS [x]
LEFT JOIN [AdvertisementPositions] AS [x.AdvertisementPosition] ON [x].[PositionId] = [x.AdvertisementPosition].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [AdvertisementPages] AS [x.AdvertisementPosition.AdvertisementPage] ON [x.AdvertisementPosition].[PageId] = [x.AdvertisementPosition.AdvertisementPage].[Id]
WHERE [x].[Status] = 1
ORDER BY [x].[SortOrder] DESC, [x].[Id], [x.AdvertisementPosition.AdvertisementPage].[Id]
OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY" (0723d8ff)

    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [x.AdvertisementPosition].[PageId], [x.AdvertisementPosition].[Name] AS [Name1], CASE
    WHEN [x.AdvertisementPosition].[PageId] IS NOT NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [x.AdvertisementPosition.AdvertisementPage].[Id] AS [Id0], [x.AdvertisementPosition.AdvertisementPage].[Name] AS [Name0]
